{"tid":677051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 中国美國爭霸策略最新分析","createTime":"2018-05-25T01:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T15:22:11.000Z","uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c8cde96e58b74e420a494eb2fc489ceb93b648d3","tid":677051,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T01:03:00.000Z","msg":"中国：<br />\n<br />\n先打大豆農產品（已取消高梁關稅調查）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再打汽車（已宣布減關稅及開放產地）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後打飛機（已經同港澳簽署協議）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n南海造地<br />\n一帶一路<br />\n削台灣邦交國<br />\n<br />\n氣勢如虹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n必贏<br />\n<br />\n美國：<br />\n先打台灣（台灣旅行法、軍事授權法案）<br />\n再打中興（商務部、國會各自出手）<br />\n打埋南海（取消邀請中国參與聯合軍演）<br />\n順手打埋北韓（指習大大係幕後黑手）<br />\n<br />\n得閒搞埋委內瑞拉、伊朗、俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n忙成咁<br />\n必輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1e5130253e7a641c6fe7734a4f3620a34db490","tid":677051,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T01:05:04.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03286b37c7c144190d2145e4cbd99dc94b2c2ba0","tid":677051,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T01:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810fbb64598afff0c76a8f77ce28a56176acbf42","tid":677051,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T01:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830773b6cb77ef654c2df941c57e80e83261395e","tid":677051,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"810fbb64598afff0c76a8f77ce28a56176acbf42","tid":677051,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislik